3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper may be relevant to the design of wireless communication networks, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper may be relevant to the transmission of multimedia content over wireless channels.
